import React, { useEffect } from 'react'
import { Redirect, Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Col, Row, Layout } from 'antd'
import LeftNav from './LeftNav'
const { Sider, Content, Header, Footer } = Layout
const PolicyRule = (props) => {
  return (
    <Layout>
      <Header theme="light" style={{ backgroundColor: '#fff' }}>
        {' '}
        <Link to={'/manage-services'}>Back to Listings</Link>
      </Header>
      <Layout>
        <Sider theme="light" className="product-menu">
          <LeftNav
            productData={
              props.location.state ? props.location.state.record : ''
            }
            id={props.location.state ? props.location.state.record._id : ''}
          />
        </Sider>
        <Content className="product-management">Policy Rule</Content>
      </Layout>
    </Layout>
  )
}
export default PolicyRule
